OL,3,CUp to #38 million to be spent on
OL,4,CDumfries Whitesands flooding
OL,5,Cprotection scheme
OL,7,FUp to #38 million is set to be spent
OL,8,Fon the Whitesands Flooding Protection
OL,9,FScheme in Dumfries.
OL,11,FDumfries and Galloway Council say that
OL,12,Fthe cash is an agreement covering both
OL,13,Fdesign development and potential
OL,14,Fconstruction phases and not a
OL,15,Fconfirmed total spend spend at this
OL,16,Fstage.
OL,18,FThe contract has been awarded to UK-
OL,19,Fbased civil engineering firm
OL,20,FMcLaughlin & Harvey following an open
OL,21,Ftender and is structured in two stages.
