OL,5,Cprotection scheme
OL,7,FStage one, which is already underway,
OL,8,Fwill see the contractor work with the
OL,9,Fcouncil to refine the scheme's
OL,10,Fdetailed design, phasing and revised
OL,11,Fcost estimates.
OL,13,FStage two is set to include the main
OL,14,Fconstruction works, including flood
OL,15,Fwalls, glass panels and gates along a
OL,16,Fnew raised riverside walkway. This
OL,17,Fphase will only proceed if explicitly
OL,18,Fapproved by councillors in December.
