OL,5,Cprotection scheme
OL,7,FDumfries and Galloway Council say that
OL,8,Fthe Whitesands Flood Protection Scheme
OL,9,Fis a major initiative to safeguard
OL,10,FDumfries town centre from the River
OL,11,FNith.
OL,13,FCllr Andy Ferguson, Chair of the
OL,14,FEconomy and Infrastructure Committee,
OL,15,Fsaid: "The Whitesands Flood Protection
OL,16,FScheme represents a vital investment
OL,17,Fin the future of Dumfries ` not only
OL,18,Fto safeguard the town centre from
OL,19,Fflooding, but also to create a
OL,20,Fvibrant, inclusive riverside space for
OL,21,Fthe community.
