OL,3,CUp to #38 million to be spent on
OL,4,CDumfries Whitesands flooding
OL,5,Cprotection scheme
OL,7,F"We understand concerns around rising
OL,8,Fcosts, and I want to reassure
OL,9,Fresidents that the project is being
OL,10,Fdeveloped with careful financial
OL,11,Foversight.
OL,13,F"A full Business Case, including
OL,14,Fdetailed costings and market testing,
OL,15,Fwill be presented to all council
OL,16,Fmembers for a decision in December
OL,17,F2025.
